{"document_id": "DOC_FD_FAQ", "title": "Radish Bank Fixed Deposit FAQ", "category": "fd_faq", "content": "# Radish Bank Fixed Deposit FAQ\n\n## Tenures and rates\n\nRadish Bank offers **6-month** and **12-month** Singapore dollar fixed deposits. Published rates match the active **FixedDepositPlan** records (for example **FD6** and **FD12**).\n\n## Minimum deposit\n\nThe minimum placement is **SGD 1,000** per plan unless a promotion states otherwise.\n\n## Interest\n\nInterest accrues for the locked tenure. At maturity, principal and interest are credited according to product rules in force on the booking date.\n\n## Early withdrawal and early termination\n\n**Early termination** (closing or **terminating** the fixed deposit before the maturity date) is the same as **early withdrawal** in this product. Withdrawing or **terminating** early may **reduce or forfeit** interest. In practice this is the **penalty** for breaking the fixed deposit early: you may lose part or all of the interest you would have earned to maturity. **Early termination penalties** are therefore interest reductions or forfeiture, not a separate cash fee in this demo. The bank applies a simple adjustment for demo purposes; always confirm the exact **penalties** or adjustments before **terminating** or breaking a deposit.\n\n## Eligibility\n\nPlacements are available from **eligible active** SGD accounts shown in the customer profile. The demo supports amounts **below SGD 10,000** per placement request.\n\n## How to book\n\nUse the in-app **place fixed deposit** flow with a chosen plan, amount, and funding account. Staff-assisted bookings in this demo follow the same validation rules.\n", "content_embedding": [-0.0030517578125, 0.0389404296875, 0.062347412109375, 0.022796630859375, -0.0218963623046875, -0.013916015625, 0.032684326171875, 0.0595703125, 0.0271453857421875, 0.0129547119140625, 0.017242431640625, -0.05096435546875, 0.0166015625, -0.055755615234375, 0.039154052734375, -0.001446723937988